column2: # It is a good practice to store all fsa files in a different folder. Maybe we should think about saving each set of files in a different folder (i.e. fsa_set1_dir, fsa_set2_dir, etc.)
fsa_dir <- "~/GitHub/peakscan/fsa"
# Reads the fsa files and stores them within a list structure
fsa_data <- storing.inds(fsa_dir, channels=5)
"Reading FSA files"
